title: Aroma Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house offering a range of labeled vegan choices for breakfast (toast, porridge), lunch (sandwiches), snack (hommus and pita), as well as children's meals. Selection of loose leave teas. Keeps soya milk on hand for tea and coffee. Sometimes vegan cake or biscuits. Has Wi-Fi, children's play area.
